dmca.title: PC Bug Doctor Software Accuses Site of Using its Serial Numbers
dmca.body:
Maximum Software Publishing 
[Private] 
[Private]

April 11, 2005 
Dear Sir or Madam:
On the Google search query, "PC Bug Doctor", sites with the URLs below http://www.moviecodec.com/topics13552p3.html 
these are on the 2nd page today


Crackspider.net! Search cracks, crackz, serial numbers, keygens ...

Crackspider.net! Search cracks, crackz, serial numbers, keygens ...
...PC Bug Doctor v1.0 by iPA serial number > PC Bug Doctor 1.0.0.3 serial number
... PC Bug Doctor v2.0 serial by iPA > Pc Bug Doctor serial ...

[listed sites illegible in scan]
CrackDB.com - pc bug doctor pc bug doctor
CrackDB.com - lagest cracks database.  Most recent updates of keygens, cracks, serials for apps, programs, and games!
crackdb.com/pc.bug.doctor/search_pc+bug+doctor_crack_keygen_serial_nocd_cracked.html - 33k - Cached - Similar pages
are being displayed in the natural search results (please see attached screenshot).
These sites are illegally providing usemame and serial number info for Maximum
Software Publishing, owner of PC Bug Doctor software (please see attached screenshot).
Contact information of infringing site (I know they haven't responded to you but please
provide the telephone number and/or email address you used to contact them)
I have a good faith belief that use of the copyrighted materials described above on the
allegedly infringing web pages is not authorized by the copyright owner, its agent, or the law.
